metadata.name: Squirreltology #1
metadata.description: Squirreltology is a life style movement, where squirrels are center of the universe, which is of course made by squirrels. Each NFT minted or sold on the first market from the community wallet comes with a custom made #squirreltology t-shirt. Second market purchases acquire the right to order a custom t-shirt, with a discount based on the height of the transaction. Each squirrel in this collection is unique hand drawn without any AI randomization. Custom designed squirrel NFTs can be ordered via twitter together with the custom t-shirt.
